{"tid":1367394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（解夢）機場都做到，唔爭在會展啦","createTime":"2019-07-26T08:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:44:30.000Z","uid":143533,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe8f32dadb92def2216525db2ddd4984c9ef1f2","tid":1367394,"uid":143533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"今日機場咁多人出黎，大陸已經好驚Ｄ大陸人接收到咩msg 再帶上去大陸。<br />\n<br />\n我發夢做過幾間公司，佢地都視會展既　美食博覽會，家居家品博覽會　為一年一度既大 project。萬一呢D 大型展覽遇上示威，佢地大多會要求黑警幫手；又或是向商界求助，傳傳下就會去到政府個邊，或者可以迫到佢地面對民情。<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢個夢係好夢定係壞夢，有冇識解夢既人一齊討論下。"},{"pid":"fa1f0924e872c491caaffba6d4b60599c6d23ca3","tid":1367394,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"唔好搞動漫節<br />\n我呢d毒撚等左成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f52e4da930fdedc4b693b866f6d39661a6cb732","tid":1367394,"uid":143533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"324231f2fdbc518441eeac454325b6b0936b162e","tid":1367394,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"334c9aff79cb7c2bb536c69dae4134089cfcfe43","tid":1367394,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa1f0924e872c491caaffba6d4b60599c6d23ca3","tid":1367394,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"唔好搞動漫節<br />\n我呢d毒撚等左成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:29:06.000Z","msg":"真係毒撚就飛日本啦<br />\n香港動漫節有乜好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd31662a5a3a9c95fe5e17f5f905eab362e312c9","tid":1367394,"uid":143533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:11:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid"